ns0:trans-unit.ns0:source: URL rewriting (mod_rewrite) is not active on your server, or it is not possible to check your server configuration. If you want to use Friendly URLs, you must activate this mod.
ns0:trans-unit.ns0:target: URL-ni qayta yozish (mod_rewrit) sizning serveringizda faol emas yoki server konfiguratsiyasini tekshirish mumkin emas.

ns0:trans-unit.ns0:source: Upload an icon from your computer (File type: .gif, suggested size: 16x16).
ns0:trans-unit.ns0:target: Iconni kompyuteringizdan yuklang (fayl turi: .gif, tavsiya etilgan hajmi: 16x16).

ns0:trans-unit.ns0:source: We recommend that you deactivate your store while performing maintenance. Note that it will not disable the webservice.
ns0:trans-unit.ns0:target: Xavfsiz ishlash paytida do'koningizni o'chirib qo'yganingizni tavsiya etamiz.

ns0:trans-unit.ns0:source: When enabled, admins will access the store front office without storing their IP.
ns0:trans-unit.ns0:target: Agar yoqilgan bo'lsa, ma'murlar do'kon old ofisiga o'z IP-ni saqlashsiz kirish huquqiga ega bo'ladilar.

ns0:trans-unit.ns0:source: When enabled, friendly URL will be updated on every name change for offline products only.
ns0:trans-unit.ns0:target: Agar yoqilgan bo'lsa, faqat oflayn mahsulotlar o'zgarishi bo'yicha har bir nomi o'zgarishi bo'yicha yangilanadi.

ns0:trans-unit.ns0:source: Whether or not to display this store.
ns0:trans-unit.ns0:target: Ushbu do'konni namoyish qilmaslik yoki bo'lmasligi kerak.

ns0:trans-unit.ns0:source: With this option enabled, it also gives the good result if you search for “lous”, “ouse”, or anything contained in the word.
ns0:trans-unit.ns0:target: Ushbu parametr bilan yoqilgan bo'lsa, shuningdek, "lous", "erni", "erni" qidirsangiz yoki so'zma-so'z mavjud bo'lgan narsani qidirsangiz yaxshi natija beradi.

ns0:trans-unit.ns0:source: With this option enabled, it only gives one result “book”, as exact end of the indexed word is matching.
ns0:trans-unit.ns0:target: Ushbu parametr bilan yoqilgan, bu faqat bitta "kitob" ni keltirib chiqaradi, chunki indekslangan so'zning aniq tugashi bilan mos keladi.

ns0:trans-unit.ns0:source: You can choose among 6 different ways of rounding prices. "Round up away from zero ..." is the recommended behavior.
ns0:trans-unit.ns0:target: Siz yaxlitlash narxlarining 6 xil usullarini tanlashingiz mumkin.

ns0:trans-unit.ns0:source: You can choose when to round prices: either on each item, each line or the total (of an invoice, for example).
ns0:trans-unit.ns0:target: Siz dumaloq narxlarda qachon: har bir elementda, har bir satrda yoki umumiy (masalan, hisob-fakturaning umumiy) tanlashingiz mumkin.

ns0:trans-unit.ns0:source: You can specify the default behavior for all disabled products. The product page can display a "Discontinued" message or an error page. You can also specify which HTTP response is sent to users. This can be set specifically for each product.
ns0:trans-unit.ns0:target: Siz barcha nogironlar uchun odatiy xatti-harakatni belgilashingiz mumkin.

ns0:trans-unit.ns0:source: You can't edit the shop group because the current shop belongs to a group with the "share" option enabled.
ns0:trans-unit.ns0:target: You can't edit the store group because the current store belongs to a group with the "share" option enabled.

ns0:trans-unit.ns0:source: [1]Make[/1] sure partner offers are not set as required in the [2]Customers[/2] section of the back office before disabling them. Otherwise, new customers won't be able to create an account and [1]proceed[/1] to checkout.
ns0:trans-unit.ns0:target: [1] [/ 1] Ishonch takliflari ularni o'chirishdan oldin [/ 2] (/ 2) bo'limida [2] rusumdagi [/ 2] bo'limida talab qilinganidek o'rnatilmagan.

ns0:trans-unit.ns0:source: characters
ns0:trans-unit.ns0:target: belgilar
